Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:37.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Run, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:46.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No... No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:49.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Captain, there's no chance! - CR}Captain, we're screwed!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There's no way to put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:57.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We gotta give up the ship!\NWe can't flee to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:03:00.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn the King!\NHow could he do this to us?! - CR}Damn that king! How could he do this to us?!{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:03.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'll show that bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:07.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:13.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's so annoying that the sky\Nin the south is bright even in the night. - CR}It's so annoying that the sky\Nin the south is bright even during the night.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:17.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We are sorry, Your Majesty.\NLet us close the curtain. -CR}Apologies, Your Majesty.\NAllow us to close the curtains.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:27.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Say, Daddy why are the people\Nin the Gray Terminal not humans? -CR}Father, is there a reason the people\Nin Gray Terminal aren't humans?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Why do they have to get burned?{CR}{And why do we need to burn them? - Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:34.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{As the phrase goes,\N"As a man sows, so shall he reap." - CR}It is said, "As a man sows, so shall he reap."{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:35.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:40.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They could have avoided their fate\Njust by being born nobles. - CR}They could have avoided their fate\Nif only they were born nobles.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Born nobles?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:48.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You're right! They should have\Nchosen to be born nobles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:50.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're stupid! - CR}How dumb of them!{LP/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:55.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, enough about those people.\NYou have to study for tomorrow. - CR}Now, enough about those people.\NYou have to study tomorrow, don't you?{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:56.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You better go to bed. - CR}You'd better get to bed.{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:58.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:18.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's no way on this side! - CR}This side's blocked, too!{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:21.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We keep losing ground. - CR}We're losing ground to stand on!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:22.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:27.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wonder if those old men escaped safely. - CR}Think those old guys got out okay?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is no time to be concerned\Nabout other people! - CR}We can't worry about anyone else right now!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:34.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn! I don't even know where I am! - CR}Crap! I don't even know where we are!{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:37.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who said that you could\Nget away, you brats?! - CR}Who said you brats could escape?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:40.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bluejam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:46.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Why are you still here after setting the fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:48.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You were supposed to have escaped by now! - CR}You should be long gone by now!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you little shit!{CR}{Shut up, you little punk! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:54.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're hopeless, you know. - CR}We're at our wits' end, you see.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:57.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We have an unforeseen dilemma. - CR}We're in a bit of a pickle.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:01.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Humans are strange creatures, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:06.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,When you hit rock bottom,\Nyou can't stop laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:16.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They are acting weird. - CR}They're being weird.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:18.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy, let's go! - CR}Luffy! We gotta run!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:20.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't let them! - CR}Stop them!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:32.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We worked together - we're friends! - CR}We worked together as crewmates, after all!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We have to die together! - CR}Now, we need to die together!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:38.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We don't wanna die with you!\NNot in a million years! - CR}We're not gonna die with you!\NNever in a million years!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:40.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're so cold. - CR}Cold shoulder, huh?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:45.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, you haven't told me\Nwhere you keep your treasure. - CR}Come to think of it, you still haven't\Ntold me where you stash your treasure.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:51.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll save it for you before the fire gets it.\NSo tell me where it is. - CR}I'll rescue it from the fire for you.\NSo, tell me where it is!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:54.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Your life is in danger and all\Nyou care about is treasure? - CR}You're about to die and all you\Ncare about is treasure?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:58.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you don't care, then tell me where it is. - CR}Well, if {\i1}you{\i0} don't care, then tell me.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:02.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You've gone mad. - CR}You've really lost it.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:06.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you're not gonna go get it, it'd be a waste. - CR}Not salvaging it would be such a waste!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:12.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If nothing is done, it's gonna be\Nreduced to charcoal like my ship. - CR}If we just stand here, it'll get\Nreduced to charcoal like my ship!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:14.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What a waste.{CR}{Truly a waste. - Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:17.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't be ridiculous! That treasure is... - CR}Don't be dumb! That treasure is–{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Alright, I tell you! - CR}Fine! I'll tell you.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:24.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ace! You and Sabo spent a lot of time... - CR}Ace! You and Sabo worked so long to–{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:26.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabo would understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:29.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What matters the most now is your... - CR}Right now your life...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:33.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What matters the most now is our lives! - CR}Right now {\i1}our{\i0} lives are more important!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:53.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We keep our treasure from\Nlast six years in this tree. - CR}We have six-years-worth\Nof treasure in this tree.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:55.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:58.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:01.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's alright. This is not the end. - CR}It's all right. This isn't where it ends.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:10.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?! I told you where it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:13.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're right. "This is not the end. - CR}You're right. "This isn't where it ends."{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:17.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Which means you could be lying.\NYou gotta come with us. -CR}There's a chance you lied,\Nso you're coming with us!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:22.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No way! Then it's gonna\Nbe too late to escape! - CR}No way! We'll lose our\Nchance to get out of here!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why don't you guys go on your own?! - CR}Just go on your own!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:31.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You don't wanna mess with me now. - CR}You don't wanna mess with me right now.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:35.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm determined to make a comeback, - CR}Even if it means robbing a few kids,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:40.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{even if it means stealing from kids so I can take my revenge on nobles. - CR}I swore I'd make a comeback\Nand get my revenge on the nobles.{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:43.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,And your brother is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:47.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,They think they're so special,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:51.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and look down on others as if we're trash! - CR}{looking down on us as if we're trash! - Z}looking down on us like\Nwe're nothing but trash!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:54.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabo doesn't think like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:57.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's the same as them, fool! - CR}He's no different, you idiot kid!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:02.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He was with you both just to feel superior! - CR}He spent time with you\Nbecause it made him feel superior!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:03.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,His parents are loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:09.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He doesn't have to\Nworry about anything! - CR}He wants for nothing!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:12.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It was just a pastime for him. - CR}This was all a cheap thrill for him.{Z}{TL FYI: He's saying it in suffering passive like "[You] were strung along in a noble's pastime/amusement"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:17.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He was looking down on you guys and laughing to himself holding his nose! - CR}He was looking down at you,\Nholding his nose while laughing to himself!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:19.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop talking bad about Sabo! - CR}Stop badmouthing Sabo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:22.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Sabo just wants to be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:26.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:26.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:32.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:38.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:44.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't touch Luffy! - CR}Don't you touch Luffy!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:15.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! You okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:24.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:26.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You creepy brat! - CR}Sneaky runt!{LP/nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:30.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you wanna make a fool out of me, too?! - CR}You looking to make a fool outta me too?!{Z}{TL: It's like "even YOU are trying to make a fool out of me?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:32.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up, you scumbag! - CR}Shut up, scumbag!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:35.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:38.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:40.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:53.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:58.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop it, you sea cretin! - CR}Stop it, you sea monster!{Z/LP}{Lit: "Umibozu" 海坊主 is a yokai called the "sea priest" or "sea monk"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:03.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Let go of Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What are you guys doing here? - CR}{You guys are here?! - Z}Why are you guys here?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:18.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Finally we found you! - CR}We finally found you!{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:22.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,These are pretty serious wounds,\NLuffy! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dogra...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:29.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I don't see Sabo anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:33.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabo went home. He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:39.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:42.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're the boss monkey from Mt. Colubo! - CR}You must be that\Nboss monkey from Mt. Colubo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:45.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm the mountain bandit, Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:49.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't know why but I'm\Nregistered as their foster parent. - CR}I'm not sure why, but for better\Nor worse, I foster these brats!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:56.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Alright then... - CR}Alright, fellas...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Run! - CR}Make a run for it!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{– Yes, boss!\N– Yes, boss! -CR}– You got it, boss!\N– You got it, boss!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:08.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:11.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:12.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:14.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I...{28:42}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,won't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:24.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What're you saying, Ace?!\NDon't try to fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:27.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bluejam's a real villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:31.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's not a guy that a kid like you can beat! - CR}Kids like you couldn't possibly\Nbeat a guy like him!{Z}{TL - It's like, "[he's] the level [of crook] that a kid can beat!" (Not exactly 'beat', but close enough)}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:32.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{L-Let me fight, too! - CR}M-Me too!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No, Luffy!
