Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:13.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you overestimate your ability,\Nyou'll only get hurt! - CR}If you overestimate your abilities,\Nyou'll pay in blood!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:18.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Only the strong and the cowardly\Nsurvive in wars! - CR}Only the strong and the cowardly\Nsurvive in battle!{Z}
