Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:24.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:26.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What a fool! - CR}Fools!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:40.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:44.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm a dead man! The fire\Nis all over the place! - CR}We're goners! The flames are all around us!{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How could this happen all of the sudden?! - CR}{It came outta nowhere! - Z}How could this happen to us?!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:49.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's hot! It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There's no way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:54.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dammit!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We have to give up! - CR}{We're not gonna make it! - Z}There's nothing we can do!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:27.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There's a path!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:29.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The explosion left a path! - CR}That explosion made a path!{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:31.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't know what's going\Non but this is great! - CR}Whatever the reason, we're in luck!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:36.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey look, there is a ship! - CR}Hey! Look! It's a ship!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I see a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:40.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,This path leads up to the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We can get away by following it! - CR}We can follow it out of here!{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:47.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's go before the fire returns! - CR}Run before the fire returns!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:55.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How awful they are to burn the\Narea and the residents there! - CR}Vhaat an awful country,\Nburning the land {\i1}and{\i0} its residents!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:57.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{By the way, - CR}By the vayy,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:14:02.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{how did you know the situation in such\Nan outlying country in the East Blue? - CR}vhyy did you know the goings on of\Nsuch a remote kingdom in the East Blue?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:06.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is there something special\Nabout this country? - CR}Vhaat is so special about this place, hm?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:10.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This country is an example of how\Nthe world will be in the future. - CR}This country is a microcosm\Nof our world's future.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:16.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There can be no happiness in a world\Nwhere the undesirables are thrown away. - CR}{No happiness can be found in a country\Nthat eliminates people they deem unnecessary. - Yibis}Happiness is but a pipe dream in a world\Nthat eliminates those deemed unnecessary.{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:21.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Someday, I will change the world! - CR}{I will change this world someday I swear it! - Yibis}I swear to you all,\NI {\i1}will{\i0} change this world someday!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:27.82,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,700)}If I stay here... I'll never be free!{CR}{I'll never be free if I stay here! - Yibis}{Flashback PW03 @41:38}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:33.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even in a country like this,\Nthere are children. - CR}{Children are born innocent,\Neven in a country like this. - Yibis}Even in a country like this,\Nchildren will be born.{LP}{TL: "Even in a country like this, children are born." or "will be born." I think he's saying either that they can't just abandon it OR that this place, too, can change}
