Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:21.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but survivors, too. - CR}{but cleaning up any survivors they find as well. - Yibis}they're "cleaning up" any survivors\Nthey find as well.{Z}
