Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:18.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's nice to know that\Nthose villains got burned! - CR}{It's a good thing those thugs were burned to death, at least. - Yibis}I'm glad those no-good thugs\Ndidn't escape the blaze.{Z/Polly}
