Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:36.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You will never get out of High Town...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:38.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{or even out of this house! - CR}much less this house!{Z}
