Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:50.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There is nothing that a nobleman can't do. - CR}Nothing is beyond a nobleman's power.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:53.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'll get the approval of your superiors.
