Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:04.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:10.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{As you know, I can make things\Nhappen just by giving the word. - CR}{As you know, my word alone is\Nenough to make things happen. - Z}As I've told you, all it takes is\Na single word to get what I want.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:14.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So I can take care of\Nyou or those two easily. - CR}Imagine what I could do to you...\Nor to your two friends.{Z}{LP - TL: "That includes you... and those two [friends of yours]."}
