Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:25.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay, have a nice day! - CR}{Well then, have a good day. - Yibis}Well then, have a wonderful day.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:37.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace... Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:42.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't think that you died in the fire. - CR}There's no way you'd\Ndie in a fire like that, right?{Yibis}
