Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.61,0:31:04.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.01,0:31:07.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop lying, you fool! - CR}You liar!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.78,0:31:09.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't even joke about it! - CR}Don't even joke about that!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.69,0:31:10.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop, Ace! - CR}{Don't do it, Ace! - Yibis}That's enough, Ace!{Nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.89,0:31:13.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying or joking about it!{CR}{It's not a lie, nor a joke! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.73,0:31:17.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It was so sudden!\NI could barely believe what I saw! - CR}{It was so sudden, I barely\Nrealized what had happened. - Yibis}It was so sudden that I doubted my own eyes!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.66,0:31:20.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I thought I was dreaming! - CR}{I wondered if it was just a dream or an illusion! - Yibis}I kept thinking it was\Nsome kind of bad dream!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.80,0:31:24.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up! Sabo went back to his family's home! - CR}{Shut up! Sabo went back to his noble born parents! - Yibis}Cut the crap! Sabo went back\Nto his noble family.{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.27,0:31:26.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,How could he be at sea?!{CR}{There's no way he'd sail out to sea! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.79,0:31:28.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right! He went home! - CR}{That's right! Sabo went home– - Yibis}That's right! Sabo went back ho–{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.74,0:31:32.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A hoodlum like me can\Nunderstand how he feels! - CR}{Outlaws like us understand\Nhow he must have felt! - Yibis}As an outlaw, I understand\Nhow he must have felt!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.07,0:31:34.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{People don't always wanna\Ngo back to their home! - CR}We all have places we really\Ndon't want to go back to!{Yibis}{Home is often the last place you wanna go! - Z}{LP - TL: I love your line, it sounds sooo good, but Yibis' is more accurate TL-wise :[}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.71,0:31:41.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If he was really happy,\Nhe wouldn't go out to sea! - CR}{Do you really think he'd go to sea...\Nif he was actually happy? - Yibis}Do you think he would've\Nset sail if he was truly happy?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.12,0:31:45.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He wouldn't go out to sea by himself\Nwith a black flag on his ship! - CR}Do you really think he'd fly\Na pirate flag and set out on his own?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.41,0:31:57.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.53,0:32:01.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He wasn't happy! - CR}He really wasn't happy!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.10,0:32:06.49,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was all by myself even if I had parents! - CR}{Even with parents, I'm still alone! - Yibis}Even with parents, I was all by myself.{Z}{PW03 @14:49}{Need fade to white effect}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.68,0:32:11.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why?! Why didn't we go\Nthere to take him back?! - CR}Why... Why didn't we try\Nto break him out of there?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.02,0:32:16.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Where is the guy who killed\NSabo now?! I'm gonna kill him! - CR}{Where is the person who killed Sabo?!\NI'm gonna murder him! - Yibis}Where's the guy who did this\Nto Sabo?! I'm gonna murder him!{Z/Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.60,0:32:19.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{K-Kill the Celestial Dragon?!\NThat's impossible... - CR}Th-The Celestial Dragon?!\NThere's no way you can do th–{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.35,0:32:20.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll make him pay! - CR}{I'm gonna avenge his death! - Yibis}I'll avenge him!{Nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.99,0:32:22.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.53,0:32:25.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop it, you little shit! - CR}{Drop it, you damn brat! - Yibis}Drop it, you little shit!{Polly - I'm just sick of "brat" especially when he's not being a "brat" something harsher is really needed here}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.76,0:32:27.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Move... - CR}Get off me...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.30,0:32:28.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Outta my way!{CR}{Don't get in my way! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.50,0:32:33.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How can you be so confident even\Nthough you're not that strong?! - CR}{You keep acting tough, even though you don't have any real strength! - Yibis}You talk pretty big for a weakling like yourself!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.04,0:32:36.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What can you do?! They'll just kill you! - CR}{What the hell do you think you can do now?! You'll just end up dead! - Yibis}What can you even do?!\NYou'll just wind up dead!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.67,0:32:41.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You'll die and people will forget you by tomorrow! You're just a nameless kid! - CR}{You'll die, and everyone will forget you by tomorrow! That's all you amount to right now! - Yibis}{\q2}You'll die, and people will forget you by tomorrow\Nbecause you still haven't amounted to anything!{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.81,0:32:47.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sabo was killed by this country! This world! - CR}{It was this kingdom that killed Sabo!\NIt was the world itself! - Yibis}It was this country—\Nthis world—that killed Sabo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.35,0:32:49.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What can you do about it?! - CR}What can {\i1}you{\i0} do?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.92,0:32:53.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Your father changed the world by his death! - CR}Your father's death brought about a new era!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.82,0:32:59.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When you become a man that important,\Nthen you can do whatever you want! - CR}{Once you become a man of his caliber,\Nthen you're free to live or die as you want! - Yibis}When you become a man of his caliber,\Nyou can die whenever the hell you please!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.63,0:33:04.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tie this fool up! - CR}{Go tie up this moron! - Yibis}Go tie this moron up!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.73,0:33:06.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!{CR}{Uh, right... - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.80,0:33:10.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.64,0:33:11.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn! - CR}Damn it!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.01,0:33:18.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}{Shut up! Stop crying like a girl, Luffy! - CR}{Shut up! Men aren't supposed to be sobbing like that, Luffy! - Yibis}Shut up! Men aren't supposed\Nto cry like that, Luffy!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.56,0:33:37.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Have you come to your senses, Ace? - CR}{Have you calmed down a little, Ace? - Yibis}Have you cooled your head a bit, Ace?{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.20,0:33:42.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Untie him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.70,0:33:43.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Yes, ma'am.\N– Yes, ma'am.{CR}{– Right.\N– Right. - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.14,0:33:46.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hold on. - CR}{I'll loosen these right away. - Yibis}{Let me loosen these. - Polly}Let me untie you.{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.81,0:33:47.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.94,0:33:49.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's been crying all night and he's sleeping now. - CR}He cried all night. He's asleep now.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.85,0:33:54.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Boss! You're not gonna believe this! - CR}Boss! You have to see this!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.85,0:33:57.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We got a letter from Sabo! - CR}I-It's a letter! From Sabo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.72,0:34:00.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He must've sent it before he went out to sea! - CR}{He sent a letter before setting out to sea! - Yibis}He must have sent a letter\Nbefore setting out to sea!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.22,0:34:02.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Give it to me! - CR}Give me that.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.19,0:34:07.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm not gonna go to the town!\NIt's for us, isn't it? - CR}I swear I won't go into the city.\NThat letter is addressed to us, right?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.74,0:34:18.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"Ace, Luffy, I hope you guys \Nweren't hurt in the fire." - CR}Ace. Luffy. I hope you weren't hurt in the fire.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.04,0:34:20.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"I'm worrying about you both but\NI believe that you're okay." - CR}{I'm worried, but I believe that you're safe. - Yibis}I'm worried, but I'm sure you're okay.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.68,0:34:27.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"I'm sorry to say it, guys, but when you\Nget this letter, I'll already be..." - CR}{I'm sorry about this, but by the time\Nyou read this letter, I'll be... - Yibis}I'm sorry, guys, but by the time you\Nget this letter, I'll already be...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.45,0:34:30.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"...out on the sea." - CR}out at sea.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.25,0:34:35.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"Things led to things and I decided\Nto set out to sea before you." - CR}{A lot has happened, and I've decided \Nto set sail ahead of you guys. - Yibis}A lot has happened, so I decided\Nto set sail ahead of you guys.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.56,0:34:44.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{"My destination will be anywhere but here." - CR}{My destination won't be in this country, but elsewhere. - Yibis}{\i1}My destination is anywhere but this country.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.83,0:34:47.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"I'm gonna become stronger..." - CR}There, I will become stronger.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.80,0:34:50.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"and become a pirate!" - CR}I'll become a pirate!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.77,0:34:54.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"The three of us have to become\Nthe freest pirates ever." - CR}{Let's become pirates with more freedom than anyone else... - Yibis}Let's become the most free pirates ever,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.18,0:34:57.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"One day, let's meet up again somewhere." - CR}{and meet up again someday.\NThe three of us. - Yibis}and then the three of us\Nshould meet up again someday.{Z}{LP - TL FYI: There's "siblings" in there, but I think incorporating it would make the line janky}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.35,0:35:03.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"Somewhere on the wide open sea!\NDefinitely, someday!" - CR}{Somewhere out on the wide, free ocean.\NI'm sure that someday, we'll meet! - Yibis}Somewhere out on the vast open sea...\NWe'll definitely meet again!{Z}{TL - He is actually saying "free"}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.19,0:35:07.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"By the way, Ace," - CR}Oh, and Ace...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.42,0:35:11.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"which of us do you think\Nis the bigger brother?" - CR}I wonder who's the older brother\Nbetween the two of us?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.26,0:35:15.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"Two big brothers and one little brother." - CR}{Two eldest sons, and one younger brother... - Yibis}Two big brothers and one little brother...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.93,0:35:20.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"It's odd but our brotherhood is my treasure." - CR}{It might be strange, but this bond\Nbetween us is my treasure. - Yibis}Maybe it's strange,\Nbut our bond is my treasure.{Z/LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.04,0:35:30.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"Luffy is still a weak crybaby but..." - CR}{Luffy might still be a weakling and a crybaby... - Yibis}Luffy might still be a weak crybaby, but...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.55,0:35:38.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"he is our little brother..." - CR}{but he's our brother! - Yibis}he's our little brother!{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.02,0:35:40.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"so take good care of him!" - CR}Take care of him for me!{Yibis}
